headline: Applied Digital Corporation (APLD) Reports Q3 Loss, Misses Revenue Estimates
summary: Applied Digital Corporation (APLD) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -45.45% and 16.75%, respectively, for the quarter ended February 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
